# Mac apps
# Some apps go stale when brew replaces the binary while running (accessibility/input-monitoring
# apps, browsers). `brew-upgrade` handles quit/restart for tagged casks:
#   restart-on-upgrade - auto quit/restart (for accessibility/input tools)
#   prompt-on-upgrade  - upgrade, then ask to restart if running (for browsers)
# Prefix with ! to temporarily disable (e.g. `# !restart-on-upgrade:`).

